{{ page.title }}
================
Implementation of Sieve of Eratosthenes. If ~~~~n~~~~ is prime, ~~~~pon[n-2] = 0~~~~

~~~~
bool pon[60];

//sieve algorithm implementation
int sieve(int n) {
    int i, j;
    for (i = 0;i < n;i++) {
        if (!pon[i]) {
            for (j = 2;(i+2)*j < n;j++) {
                pon[(i+2)*j - 2] = 1;
            }
        }
    }
    return 1;
}
~~~~
